(deflayermap (gaming)
  2 1  3 2  4 3  5 4  6 5  7 6  8 7  9 8  0 9  - 0
  q tab  w q  e w  r e  t r  y t  u y   i u  o i  p o [ p
  a lsft  s a  d s  f d  g f  h g  l h  k j  j k  ; l
  < lctl z z  x x  c c  v v
  f12 (layer-switch colemak-dh-wider-plusplus)
)


